[2026-07-01T15:13:46.669Z] [INFO] [stdout] - `prompts/` — per-domain prompt builders with versioning (`explain.ts`, `vocabulary.ts`, `article.ts`, `video.ts`, `dictionary.ts`); prompts are no longer inline in HTTP-calling code
