[2026-07-01T15:13:46.670Z] [INFO] [stdout] **Design patterns applied:**
[2026-07-01T15:13:46.670Z] [INFO] [stdout] - **Dependency Inversion** — client depends on adapter interface, not concrete implementation
[2026-07-01T15:13:46.670Z] [INFO] [stdout] - **Adapter Pattern** — `AIAdapter` interface decouples the client from provider implementations
[2026-07-01T15:13:46.670Z] [INFO] [stdout] - **Separation of Concerns** — prompts, validation, HTTP, and business logic are in separate modules
[2026-07-01T15:13:46.670Z] [INFO] [stdout] - **DRY** — eliminated 5 duplicate `callAI`/`extractJSON`/`ProviderConfig` definitions across old files
